<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM1.8">
<l>vētiyaṉai vētap poruḷāṉai vētattuk</l>
<l>kātiyaṉai yātirainaṉ ṉāḷāṉaic cōtippāṉ</l>
<l>vallēṉa māyppukku mālavaṉu māṭṭātu</l>
<l>killēṉa māveṉṟāṉ kīḻ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In order to illuminate him who is the Veda, the meaning of the Veda,</l>
<l>the beginning of the Veda, him whose good day is Ātirai</l>
<l>Māl himself too entered as a strong hog [and] said from below:</l>
<l>“alas, I can’t, I am not able.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
